    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_msg_duration_desc">
        <text>How long the ammo status message stays on screen (in seconds).</text>
    </string>

    <!-- HUD Settings -->
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_hidecounter">
        <text>Hide Ammo Counter</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_hidecounter_desc">
        <text>Hide the default HUD ammo counter for a more immersive experience.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_hideicon">
        <text>Hide Ammo Icon</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_hideicon_desc">
        <text>Hide the ammo type icon from the HUD.</text>
    </string>

    <!-- Behavior Settings -->
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_check_grenade_mode">
        <text>Check in Grenade Mode</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_check_grenade_mode_desc">
        <text>Allow ammo checking while the weapon is in grenade launcher mode.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_auto_check_reload">
        <text>Auto-Check After Reload</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_auto_check_reload_desc">
        <text>Automatically display ammo status after completing a reload.</text>
    </string>

    <!-- Animation Settings -->
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_enable_animations">
        <text>Enable Animations</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_enable_animations_desc">
        <text>Master switch for all animations. When OFF, only the text message will be displayed (no weapon animations).</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_anim_mode">
        <text>Alternative Mag Inspect Animation</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_anim_mode_desc">
        <text>Animation for weapons WITHOUT proper mag inspect animation. Default: hide/show weapon. Lower Weapon: lower weapon briefly. Fake Reload: play reload animation for magazine weapons, special animations for internal magazine weapons.</text>
    </string>
    <!-- Animation Mode List Options -->
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_anim_mode_lst_anim_mode_default">
        <text>Default (Hide/Show)</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_anim_mode_lst_anim_mode_lower">
        <text>Lower Weapon</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_anim_mode_lst_anim_mode_fake_reload">
        <text>Fake Reload</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_no_magazine_fallback">
        <text>No Magazine Fallback</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_no_magazine_fallback_desc">
        <text>Animation when using Fake Reload mode and NO magazine is loaded (MagsRedux detachable mag weapons only). Hide/Show: switch weapon. Lower: lower weapon. None: just show message.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_fallback">
        <text>Internal Mag Fallback</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_fallback_desc">
        <text>Fallback animation for internal magazine weapons (shotguns, revolvers, etc.) not in special lists when using Fake Reload mode.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_no_magazine_fallback_lst_fallback_hide_show">
        <text>Hide/Show Weapon</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_no_magazine_fallback_lst_fallback_lower">
        <text>Lower Weapon</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_no_magazine_fallback_lst_fallback_none">
        <text>None (Message Only)</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_fallback_lst_fallback_hide_show">
        <text>Hide/Show Weapon</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_fallback_lst_fallback_lower">
        <text>Lower Weapon</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_empty_mag_fallback">
        <text>Empty Magazine Fallback</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_empty_mag_fallback_desc">
        <text>Animation to play when checking ammo with an empty magazine inserted. "Reload Animation" plays the full reload animation without actually loading ammo. "Animate" tries anm_bore/anm_idle. "Lower Weapon" just lowers the weapon briefly.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_empty_mag_fallback_lst_empty_mag_reload_anim">
        <text>Reload Animation</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_empty_mag_fallback_lst_empty_mag_animate">
        <text>Animate (anm_bore/idle)</text>
    </string>
    <string id="rax_ammo_check_empty_mag_fallback_lst_empty_mag_lower">
        <text>Lower Weapon</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_treat_one_chamber_as_non_empty">
        <text>Treat 1 in a Chamber as Non-Empty Mag</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_treat_one_chamber_as_non_empty_desc">
        <text>By default (OFF), a weapon with only 1 round left (just the chambered round, magazine itself empty) plays anm_ammo_check_empty - the magazine is empty after all. Enable this to revert to the engine default: anm_ammo_check (full inspect) still plays because total ammo > 0. Only affects weapons that define anm_ammo_check_empty in their HUD config.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_bolt_cycle">
        <text>Bolt-Action: Cycle Bolt</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_bolt_cycle_desc">
        <text>For INTERNAL-mag bolt-action rifles (Kar98, Mosin, etc.) play bolt open/close animation instead of fallback. Does not affect external-mag variants (see option below).</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_force_bolt_cycle_external_mag">
        <text>Force Bolt Cycle for External-Mag Rifles</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_force_bolt_cycle_external_mag_desc">
        <text>By default, bolt-action rifles with detachable magazines (L96A1, Remington 700, K98 Mauser Kit, etc.) play fake reload (anm_reload). Enable this to force them to play the explicit bolt cycle animation (anm_open/anm_close) instead. Useful if you prefer consistent bolt-cycling for all bolt-action rifles regardless of magazine type.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_bolt_eject">
        <text>Bolt-Action: Eject Round</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_bolt_eject_desc">
        <text>Just like in real life. When cycling the bolt, eject one round from the magazine (adds to inventory). Requires "Cycle Bolt" to be enabled. Not all bolt-action rifles supported.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_pump_rack">
        <text>Pump-Action: Rack Slide</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_pump_rack_desc">
        <text>For pump-action shotguns (Remington 870, etc.) play pump open/close animation instead of fallback.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_pump_eject">
        <text>Pump-Action: Eject Shell</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_pump_eject_desc">
        <text>Just like in real life. When racking the slide, eject one shell from the magazine (adds to inventory). Requires "Rack Slide" to be enabled. Not all pump-action shotguns supported.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_ignore_list">
        <text>Fake Reload Ignore Some Weapons</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_fake_reload_ignore_list_desc">
        <text>Use blacklist to skip fake reload animations for weapons with non-immersive or broken animations. Affected weapons will use the fallback animation instead. Edit ammo_check_weapons.script to customize the list.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_busy_hands_delay">
        <text>Message Delay</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_busy_hands_delay_desc">
        <text>Delay before showing the message (in seconds).</text>
    </string>

    <!-- Keybind Settings -->
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_keybind">
        <text>Ammo Check Key</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_keybind_desc">
        <text>Key to press for checking ammo. Can be combined with modifier keys.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_update_mcm">
        <text>Update MCM to change keybind here. Key defaults to T.</text>
    </string>

    <!-- Debug Settings -->
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_debug_mode">
        <text>Debug Mode</text>
    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_rax_ammo_check_debug_mode_desc">
        <text>Enable debug mode for animation testing. When ON: Numpad 0-9 tests weapon states, Numpad * lists weapon animations. Use to discover which state triggers bolt cycling.</text>
    </string>
</string_table>
